        "content": "<p>Is there any way to prove this?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ha</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hb</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
