        "content": "<p>You're dividing by 0 on the right hand side -- is this what you mean to do? I doubt the goal is provable (becaue 1/0=0 in Lean), but I also doubt it's what you actually mean to do.</p>",
        "id": 420911435,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1707676167
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This will be false: the left hand side is positive, but the right hand side is (defined to be) zero.</p>",
        "id": 420911610,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Stoll",
        "timestamp": 1707676305
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes that is what I meant to do. I wanted to see if it was possible.</p>",
